title: 690. Deep Dive on College QB Prospects at Manning Passing Academy
itunes:title: 690. Deep Dive on College QB Prospects at Manning Passing Academy
description:
Bucky Brooks and special guest Rhett Lewis are back with a new episode of Move the Sticks. On this show, the guys do a deep dive on the top college quarterback prospects, who will be counselors at the upcoming Manning Passing Academy (2:25). They also touch on previous quarterbacks who participated in the camp that went on to the NFL. Move the Sticks is a part of the NFL Podcasts Network.

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
